        "title": {
          "type": "text",
          "$t": "Detva - Kalamárka 3 D"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "html",
          "$t": "<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;V máji nás oslovil šikovný 3D grafik Matej Haulík s projektom 3D vizualizácie možného vzhľadu slovanského hradiska <a href=\"http://www.hradiska.sk/search/label/Detva%20-%20Kalam%C3%A1rka\">Detva - Kalamárka</a>. Mnohé veci už mal naštudované, s niektorými detailami sme poradili, požiadal som o pomoc s 3D modelom reliéfu Dr. Tibora Lieskovského a tiež sme poprosili o konzultácie pána Dr. Petra Šalkovského z AU SAV, ktorý na hradisku robil výskum. Všetkým zúčastneným patrí naša vďaka a veľmi ma teší, že môžem touto formou predstaviť ďalšie 3D slovanské hradisko. </p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTnR8Gok5Jv7zfIwFWbMlIzU1T3hDeSScMBIaA_W7QuWPLW__zVBcRzTLgyLzLc6dDPQdyIyUgavcTP3XHcwqtcAw43DZwc93PXnQr9srGOVrOA4caIEAxl4WvejgdBbny04ds3yPmHJ8m/s1920/fortificationfinaledit.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiTnR8Gok5Jv7zfIwFWbMlIzU1T3hDeSScMBIaA_W7QuWPLW__zVBcRzTLgyLzLc6dDPQdyIyUgavcTP3XHcwqtcAw43DZwc93PXnQr9srGOVrOA4caIEAxl4WvejgdBbny04ds3yPmHJ8m/s320/fortificationfinaledit.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj6z_NpcTcUbolfXOpGYp2CTbpn6kxoFwdDWuMDa-mdcSJCkHiphXUjl4aKHVYO1km3jzNhWz1rZouVD6olTeFSSDFKBw6L68ucB6ykbRVuKp_508Aw9AgPzzl5g237yJEajld55ZarOTVV/s1920/fhggrtzrrhgfgh.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEj6z_NpcTcUbolfXOpGYp2CTbpn6kxoFwdDWuMDa-mdcSJCkHiphXUjl4aKHVYO1km3jzNhWz1rZouVD6olTeFSSDFKBw6L68ucB6ykbRVuKp_508Aw9AgPzzl5g237yJEajld55ZarOTVV/s320/fhggrtzrrhgfgh.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Čo sa týka modelu samotného kopca, vychádzali sme ako som už naznačil, z LIDARového modelu, ktorý nám poskytol Tibor Lieskovský, čo veľmi pomohlo. Po väčšine obvodu hradiska sa nezachoval drevozemný val, pretože by ani nemal logický zmysel, keďže hradisko stojí na vysokej skale s kolmými bralami. Lepšie prístupná bola iba z juhovýchodu. Práve tam postavili Slovania pevný drevozemný val a bránu.&nbsp; Po obvode ostatných&nbsp; častí hradiska možno predpokladať nanajvýš ohradu z dôvodu bezpečnosti pre ľudí a zvieratá.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiGd-twhUs1uaVkZ9Bf5TMDWN-AC8I05LnO3zURq0PwCEjSuaWIixPJcBm4e6PTr3jSAQTmKFcUjMAztv7dMWawlUwVPTNsV4x7OKsU7ZiYiZnNV073r3g8Tb6HIRGZqgYduMZaAQqY6JqE/s1920/wholerzturathnfgr.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiGd-twhUs1uaVkZ9Bf5TMDWN-AC8I05LnO3zURq0PwCEjSuaWIixPJcBm4e6PTr3jSAQTmKFcUjMAztv7dMWawlUwVPTNsV4x7OKsU7ZiYiZnNV073r3g8Tb6HIRGZqgYduMZaAQqY6JqE/s320/wholerzturathnfgr.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgJIQPgy9OjnRjjzXjOok9jaQd3xS0arJZ6qm_-hj0wsyGqgkgx6dxMQVW-tJoFTQxSEjQK2f1OAyURIZGQhc-vd6KcmiiAUG1VaxMTKNYvcRG0_Vf280fENOOTpt0s31cED3Ta56uJdacm/s1920/wholerzopravenatexturathfgr.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgJIQPgy9OjnRjjzXjOok9jaQd3xS0arJZ6qm_-hj0wsyGqgkgx6dxMQVW-tJoFTQxSEjQK2f1OAyURIZGQhc-vd6KcmiiAUG1VaxMTKNYvcRG0_Vf280fENOOTpt0s31cED3Ta56uJdacm/s320/wholerzopravenatexturathfgr.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjenW9sG2yhjSWCzsHhjlwFIWVEyzp-mzFiYE2D1zIbIikfh84uJViznSbL8TCSZLPVkfT0PTvf4aKOC3VNTPtc_UPICNu47KRT1f0_zQbr47v1xW56-V2K3Q3Ji1Zr533AIMJEZ1URa7W6/s1920/whole1.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjenW9sG2yhjSWCzsHhjlwFIWVEyzp-mzFiYE2D1zIbIikfh84uJViznSbL8TCSZLPVkfT0PTvf4aKOC3VNTPtc_UPICNu47KRT1f0_zQbr47v1xW56-V2K3Q3Ji1Zr533AIMJEZ1URa7W6/s320/whole1.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgXINvnIXA6KPBVtm10Nkb9vgwiDDsarTSnOKKxU75m5JgTejgboortxNqwrD9PmhfwPFlgsoLoIABuWTB_zc4iBcALIj1wUBhPqCLZa3-v1dcynjuZSEegvk1hok0ySbJngaGsY4YyWuJb/s1920/whole3.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgXINvnIXA6KPBVtm10Nkb9vgwiDDsarTSnOKKxU75m5JgTejgboortxNqwrD9PmhfwPFlgsoLoIABuWTB_zc4iBcALIj1wUBhPqCLZa3-v1dcynjuZSEegvk1hok0ySbJngaGsY4YyWuJb/s320/whole3.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vnútornú zástavbu tvoria typické slovanské malé zrubové stavby, jedna z nich má väčšie rozmery, nakoľko v nej predpokladáme obydlie pána hradu. Okrem toho sú na hradisku tiež hospodárske stavby. Dr. Šalkovský nás upozornil, že&nbsp; výskum nepreukázal takú hustú zástavbu, ako sme vymodelovali, ale pri nadzemných stavbách nezahĺbených do zeme je to niekedy ťažko preukázať.</p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Drevená modla je autorova fantázia, nemáme ju archeologicky doloženú, ale myslím že hradisko zaujímavo oživila. <br /></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjI4wB_fNpKQ0waUn24hpqO7p_k8GUjK5VLqoQsxdnHNz1nxYhObvWhbY56dGUKG3YGDPD2v20Dbs8fzawYHnaC6XDIz7ufIzhx9Y6WRVLQi1nkLcWZjwSQqkFcWA5_d31ZSOsNtw36lJR3/s1920/houses1.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjI4wB_fNpKQ0waUn24hpqO7p_k8GUjK5VLqoQsxdnHNz1nxYhObvWhbY56dGUKG3YGDPD2v20Dbs8fzawYHnaC6XDIz7ufIzhx9Y6WRVLQi1nkLcWZjwSQqkFcWA5_d31ZSOsNtw36lJR3/s320/houses1.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiolKeyVP6smOVMTc5HKyQu-QCRqj_ydnTvoyXtNfhskfqOFGzQ-C-OvVAZoxSLlI_kI4KI4tzLlUJMZRstZX7MKHmAbEC0ds9B3jhhY3xR48EYlS-NpeJWBl62UV1_YkM8h4CSdCmy1Fqi/s1920/podmurovkamodlar.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEiolKeyVP6smOVMTc5HKyQu-QCRqj_ydnTvoyXtNfhskfqOFGzQ-C-OvVAZoxSLlI_kI4KI4tzLlUJMZRstZX7MKHmAbEC0ds9B3jhhY3xR48EYlS-NpeJWBl62UV1_YkM8h4CSdCmy1Fqi/s320/podmurovkamodlar.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjfD0TIu8Bfy60w0I0btXpkDc6hKIIdwmUzPHQTxb-S8YMHLmsb7N8GhIi9h2V637gEk_sbkN23x-rt0ySEq7uD-PBh-dYk8wiEDoTlQTC9x9jQ0ruWkHhiP50EWddA8i5yVm1e2kyJt9IR/s1920/withzforest25.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjfD0TIu8Bfy60w0I0btXpkDc6hKIIdwmUzPHQTxb-S8YMHLmsb7N8GhIi9h2V637gEk_sbkN23x-rt0ySEq7uD-PBh-dYk8wiEDoTlQTC9x9jQ0ruWkHhiP50EWddA8i5yVm1e2kyJt9IR/s320/withzforest25.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjFgn3TqiK5SqGSpI9ZltF2-ABxfQnOWsOQRb1mLex0GyNVDwdlNHtBRgwINPwoY5IGEULGF9llG7quft9GWz8qN9KtJqe5jMxwRPE9QbaXUZcDFVxf2bgGAlFlIr9Gy1llp2n0owsstdIf/s1920/zatupenepalisadnnmnsyfdd.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEjFgn3TqiK5SqGSpI9ZltF2-ABxfQnOWsOQRb1mLex0GyNVDwdlNHtBRgwINPwoY5IGEULGF9llG7quft9GWz8qN9KtJqe5jMxwRPE9QbaXUZcDFVxf2bgGAlFlIr9Gy1llp2n0owsstdIf/s320/zatupenepalisadnnmnsyfdd.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgJaEw6u9Isn7Z_znM9f8MZquEjm9iUhdnIeh_wBFiPkJdiaL6rOc8WixBzvSPijYJe81xvYgb2T6XklY8n3lFywQHpnw5oVVVKppH4pcNhVHlZKm_5yEDJ934fSoA8ZqXDG6MmrKexQqma/s1920/fhggrrhgfgh.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgJaEw6u9Isn7Z_znM9f8MZquEjm9iUhdnIeh_wBFiPkJdiaL6rOc8WixBzvSPijYJe81xvYgb2T6XklY8n3lFywQHpnw5oVVVKppH4pcNhVHlZKm_5yEDJ934fSoA8ZqXDG6MmrKexQqma/s320/fhggrrhgfgh.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh6Z7erpqQrHqCKmbsU6aBzNJUsFHPFUGrm5IP9VpptBm2X43nhwAkXoJyhseguqEe2pLjQWGBT8F01SJ2v9TZBAQuvoGnB5giP4dC00JH3aGBoIreIBeV2pTKAwc2D4m5VWx_aR140ZMHh/s1920/fhghgfgh.png\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1920\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEh6Z7erpqQrHqCKmbsU6aBzNJUsFHPFUGrm5IP9VpptBm2X43nhwAkXoJyhseguqEe2pLjQWGBT8F01SJ2v9TZBAQuvoGnB5giP4dC00JH3aGBoIreIBeV2pTKAwc2D4m5VWx_aR140ZMHh/s320/fhghgfgh.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>&nbsp;Orgoň<br /><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br /></p><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgQvIxOFHP9Beaxzt-Lcs1hKbV3nmnvulumZyCp5hRmVGQkGpTm5ZeAPA6HcF7Qsozxt5L9IiR5j9In_4l2BGzw03UCw45v9qjznGGn6BVljmwX3J4S14NBLbaHmjV6770JAggnHiolzMbB/s1864/Capturekjala.PNG\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1050\" data-original-width=\"1864\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgQvIxOFHP9Beaxzt-Lcs1hKbV3nmnvulumZyCp5hRmVGQkGpTm5ZeAPA6HcF7Qsozxt5L9IiR5j9In_4l2BGzw03UCw45v9qjznGGn6BVljmwX3J4S14NBLbaHmjV6770JAggnHiolzMbB/s320/Capturekjala.PNG\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br /><div class=\"separator\" style=\"clear: both; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgC0gFnAUWGLRHKyj3ZetKizJC6PVgWqgjYjtTLaPF7sRDOBTPqP93rQHpk1u2xL0aeyXgwUd1fe6voi7R_5rn5SYlfkS-G-LDz9VhKAzM2VdXqspIf82S8twbsva5oHDy7Wg9OCAidaTxQ/s1919/fefeefefghtled.png\" imageanchor=\"1\" style=\"margin-left: 1em; margin-right: 1em;\"><img border=\"0\" data-original-height=\"1080\" data-original-width=\"1919\" src=\"https://blogger.googleusercontent.com/img/b/R29vZ2xl/AVvXsEgC0gFnAUWGLRHKyj3ZetKizJC6PVgWqgjYjtTLaPF7sRDOBTPqP93rQHpk1u2xL0aeyXgwUd1fe6voi7R_5rn5SYlfkS-G-LDz9VhKAzM2VdXqspIf82S8twbsva5oHDy7Wg9OCAidaTxQ/s320/fefeefefghtled.png\" width=\"320\" /></a></div><br />"
